column5: I got out on a small, but deep lake on Sunday. The warmest surface water I measured was 65 F and it looked like the lake was starting to turn. It's going to be an early fall on the water.
Yep same here. Was reading 63F on Kashag this weekend. Trees haven't changed much though.
I was up in Wilberforce area this weekend and the water was 57 degrees!
